<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="313">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$huang-jun-lin-15" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/huang-jun-lin-15" class="zg-link" title="Dawlin">Dawlin</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-meng-yu-70-62" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-meng-yu-70-62" class="zg-link" title="失踪已久的安女神">失踪已久的安女神</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lei-ling-95" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lei-ling-95" class="zg-link" title="雷零">雷零</a></span>
